title: American Queen's visit to Hannibal today cancelled
text: American Queen’s visit to Hannibal today cancelled Today’s scheduled visit of the American Queen to Hannibal has been cancelled due to high water that made it impossible for the riverboat to pass beneath some bridges in the St. Louis area. Comment   Writer Posted Jul. 20, 2015 at 9:28 AM Posted Jul. 20, 2015 at 9:28 AM HANNIBAL Today’s scheduled visit of the American Queen to Hannibal has been cancelled due to high water that made it impossible for the riverboat to pass beneath some bridges in the St. Louis area. In addition, the Saturday, Aug. 1, docking in Hannibal is also cancelled as it would have been the American Queen’s return trip.   Writer
